WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.560 --> 00:00:02.399
Well, I'm glad you're all here tonight.

00:00:02.399 --> 00:00:03.288
Thank you for joining us.

00:00:03.288 --> 00:00:07.520
I always have to do it like this, you know: 'Good morning, family.

00:00:07.520 --> 00:00:10.187
' But it's evening now.

00:00:11.040 --> 00:00:13.652
I appreciate you all being here tonight, I really do.

00:00:13.652 --> 00:00:18.720
I feel an urgency to pray, so let's pray together as a family.

00:00:19.004 --> 00:00:26.311
The Lord put it very strong in my heart about the 14th going through the 6th of July.

00:00:26.311 --> 00:00:28.959
And this is a very serious time.

00:00:28.959 --> 00:00:38.560
I told you yesterday—well, in my prayer time yesterday, the video came up today—I felt that the strikes against Iran were imminent.

00:00:38.560 --> 00:00:43.120
And I said I feel very urgent about this, and I tried to warn you all.

00:00:43.120 --> 00:00:51.120
There are things I was shown in the spirit about the attacks on Iran, and I saw...

00:00:51.120 --> 00:00:56.097
You know, I'm not used to doing live videos, y'all, so I filter a lot of things.

00:00:56.097 --> 00:00:57.689
My son will, you know, I can't.

00:00:57.689 --> 00:01:00.740
So this is just life, this is what's so wild.

00:01:00.740 --> 00:01:03.140
I go, 'Okay, here I go.

00:01:03.140 --> 00:01:19.430
' The things the Lord showed me about secret meetings—God protect me—with, I saw Little Kim, Russia, and certain major powers, I'll say it like that.

00:01:19.430 --> 00:01:32.267
I saw certain major powers that were devising a plan in the days ahead to come and strike, like react against what Israel just did today.

00:01:32.267 --> 00:01:34.613
And you know what's interesting, folks?

00:01:34.613 --> 00:01:43.982
Whenever I was praying over that last night, the Lord was showing me Israel with hidden technological advancements that nobody had in the world.

00:01:43.982 --> 00:01:57.817
And the Lord spoke to me and He said, 'The United States of America doesn't even know what they have from the past administration, Joe Biden and them.

00:01:57.817 --> 00:01:59.520
' He said, 'Brandon, they didn't even know.

00:01:59.520 --> 00:02:02.057
' And He said, 'And Trump barely knows.

00:02:02.057 --> 00:02:07.360
They have great technological advancements,' is what the Lord showed me.

00:02:07.360 --> 00:02:21.508
And I saw, He told me about the pagers again and the cell phones, what they did and how they caused all that to happen back—I don't remember when it was, but it's deeper than this.

00:02:21.508 --> 00:02:27.360
And the Lord said, 'Pray, for Ezekiel 38 and 39 is right at your door.

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:31.409
' Now, in the time scheme of things, I don't know what that means.

00:02:31.409 --> 00:02:42.044
You know, a thousand days is to the Lord like one day, so it's not like it could be tomorrow, it could be six months from now, I don't know.

00:02:42.382 --> 00:02:48.800
But it's something that we should be watching, that we see Ezekiel 38 and 39, and it's getting ready to happen.

00:02:48.800 --> 00:02:51.244
And I'm telling you, I didn't see Syria in this.

00:02:51.244 --> 00:02:56.987
I saw Turkey, I saw Pakistan, I saw them—I saw them upset.

00:02:56.987 --> 00:03:00.818
I'm not saying they're a part of Ezekiel; I have to make that clear.

00:03:00.818 --> 00:03:05.640
But I saw them upset in the days ahead.

00:03:05.640 --> 00:03:06.720
I saw Afghanistan.

00:03:06.720 --> 00:03:07.897
I saw Pakistan.

00:03:07.897 --> 00:03:17.360
I saw other nations that were very upset about what happened today, tonight, or whatever is going on right now.

00:03:17.360 --> 00:03:22.178
So we pray because I told you all about the great Apollyon coming up out of the pit.

00:03:22.178 --> 00:03:26.426
I said he turns around like a dust devil on the land, causing war.

00:03:26.426 --> 00:03:32.830
And I saw the great Apollyon coming out of the pit spinning, and he went around and started to spin around Putin.

00:03:32.830 --> 00:03:36.183
And I said, 'In the days ahead, you'll see this stuff coming.

00:03:36.183 --> 00:03:40.629
' I warned everybody, but even today it was like confirmation.

00:03:40.629 --> 00:03:45.200
You know, some of the things people say I missed it so big on about the Asian man.

00:03:45.200 --> 00:03:50.000
I saw an Asian man rising up in the Catholic Church.

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:52.679
I said, 'There's an Asian man, and I don't know if this is a pope or not.

00:03:52.679 --> 00:03:53.857
' I said, 'I don't know what I'm seeing.

00:03:53.857 --> 00:03:58.899
I try to be as transparent with y'all as I can be when I'm praying, and I tell you what I'm seeing.

00:03:58.899 --> 00:04:00.000
I see an Asian man.

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:16.479
He's rising up in Asia and he will be part of the Catholic Church like a pope, but he's going to try to bring a revival, trying to create excitement in the Catholic Church in the days ahead.

00:04:16.479 --> 00:04:19.359
' That Asian man was announced today.

00:04:19.359 --> 00:04:20.439
It happened weeks later.

00:04:20.439 --> 00:04:26.187
But even when I told you all, I said it will happen in the summer months.

00:04:27.698 --> 00:04:31.040
I saw June, July, August, September, October.

00:04:31.040 --> 00:04:40.177
And I said then I saw a route coming up out of the sky going down into the Vatican, where the pope was announced.

00:04:40.177 --> 00:04:49.253
And I saw it hit the courtyard there, and it splintered out, and I saw a spirit come on this Asian man.

00:04:49.253 --> 00:04:54.720
And I said, 'I don't know what I'm seeing, but the Lord told me to pray about this.

00:04:54.720 --> 00:04:56.627
' And then we see an Asian man rise up today.

00:04:56.627 --> 00:05:01.519
And I just think that's interesting because, I'm telling you, folks, Jesus Christ is coming.

00:05:01.519 --> 00:05:07.520
A great revival is about to happen, but a great shaking to awaken is about to happen.

00:05:07.520 --> 00:05:11.039
I told you about the ten cities to pray.

00:05:11.039 --> 00:05:12.119
Now, there's a lot of people...

00:05:12.119 --> 00:05:14.479
Can you put up the article so they can see?

00:05:14.773 --> 00:05:15.947
Okay, thank you, son.

00:05:15.947 --> 00:05:17.000
I appreciate that.

00:05:17.000 --> 00:05:29.714
But I see what the Lord is warning me to pray over: these on the 14th, the military parade, and interceding and praying over Donald, his grandchildren.

00:05:29.714 --> 00:05:40.251
I saw especially Kai, to intercede for this young woman to pray a hedge of protection around her that no weapon formed against her would prosper.

00:05:40.251 --> 00:05:43.565
I pray over his children, and I pray over Trump Towers.

00:05:43.565 --> 00:05:46.720
We must pray for these things.

00:05:46.720 --> 00:05:50.600
The enemy, you know, we wrestle not against flesh and blood, ladies and gentlemen.

00:05:50.600 --> 00:05:55.280
We wrestle against principalities and powers and spiritual wickedness in high places.

00:05:55.280 --> 00:06:00.360
We're not dealing with the people; we're dealing with the demonic spirits influencing them.

00:06:00.360 --> 00:06:07.000
And that's why I said I don't have authority in your neighborhood to pray over your area, but you do.

00:06:07.000 --> 00:06:10.226
And that's why the Lord said, 'Brandon, raise up.

00:06:10.226 --> 00:06:20.800
I'm raising up a million-man and woman prayer army on your channel to pray, and you will change things as you pray and intercede for the nations.

00:06:20.800 --> 00:06:25.552
' And so we see the things happening with Israel right now, and this is very serious.

00:06:25.552 --> 00:06:30.354
I saw great antisemitism coming in the days ahead.

00:06:30.354 --> 00:06:31.509
Great, very bad.

00:06:31.509 --> 00:06:38.382
And I saw that Trump would be diplomatic: 'We can't, I don't want to, you know, we're going to try to work this out.

00:06:38.382 --> 00:06:44.319
' But I saw Bibi pushing the button, exactly what happened.

00:06:44.319 --> 00:06:51.759
If you go to what I told you all, what I said in prayer yesterday, I saw to pray for Cuba.

00:06:51.759 --> 00:06:57.420
I'm watchful over what I say because I'm live now, but you can go watch it yourself.

00:06:58.080 --> 00:07:03.199
Pray about Cuba, and I saw mules.

00:07:03.199 --> 00:07:06.560
I heard the word 'mules' coming at night.

00:07:06.560 --> 00:07:10.400
I saw strategic things...

00:07:12.400 --> 00:07:13.644
How do I say that?

00:07:13.644 --> 00:07:18.986
I just don't feel peace about saying that right now live.

00:07:18.986 --> 00:07:20.587
No, I don't think that's...

00:07:21.120 --> 00:07:24.240
It's already on the internet, but I'm not saying that.

00:07:24.240 --> 00:07:26.000
But we should...

00:07:26.000 --> 00:07:33.189
Okay, we should just be praying over what I told you all to pray over concerning Cuba.

00:07:33.199 --> 00:07:37.360
Is this what I warned you all about?

00:07:37.360 --> 00:07:52.044
Not terrorist activity, but an influx of what came across the border over the past four years was a whole bunch of people from another country that was an army.

00:07:52.044 --> 00:08:02.400
And I saw men rising up, and they were like cells of people in ten major cities.

00:08:02.400 --> 00:08:03.390
Very serious stuff.

00:08:03.390 --> 00:08:05.831
I saw things on fire, and I saw...

00:08:06.095 --> 00:08:12.400
I told you about the vans, I told you about the trucks clear back in January, the timing and me interceding.

00:08:12.627 --> 00:08:18.525
You know, whenever you're seeing in the spirit, it looks like it's right in front of your face.

00:08:18.525 --> 00:08:26.879
It's like it's tomorrow, but you're praying about something that's sometimes months away.

00:08:26.879 --> 00:08:30.560
And I've warned you to pray over the summer months.

00:08:30.560 --> 00:08:38.149
This is a very serious time to pray over the summer months, praying for America, praying for peace over this nation.

00:08:38.149 --> 00:08:41.040
So, I don't know, folks.

00:08:41.040 --> 00:08:44.704
It's just a very interesting time.

00:08:45.440 --> 00:08:48.880
Is everybody here?

00:08:48.880 --> 00:08:49.630
We have 21...

00:08:49.630 --> 00:08:50.880
Well, let's praise the Lord.

00:08:50.880 --> 00:08:53.909
I'm glad you all decided to join us for prayer tonight.

00:08:53.909 --> 00:08:56.080
But let's just pray.

00:08:56.080 --> 00:08:57.439
You know, I've done enough talking.

00:08:57.439 --> 00:09:00.217
I don't want to sit and ramble and waste y'all's time.

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:03.592
What I had to say is what I had to say.

00:09:03.592 --> 00:09:07.250
But just to warn you, I have such an urgency to pray for the Fourth of July.

00:09:07.250 --> 00:09:09.775
I kept telling you I see those half-flags.

00:09:10.367 --> 00:09:11.510
I saw the flags.

00:09:11.510 --> 00:09:12.613
I saw the baby.

00:09:12.613 --> 00:09:15.827
I saw all these things, and to intercede.

00:09:15.827 --> 00:09:19.120
And the Lord said, "I'm bringing unity in the body of Christ.

00:09:19.120 --> 00:09:21.453
I'm bringing down racial barriers.

00:09:21.453 --> 00:09:26.880
" He said, "Brandon, you must be united like it was in Acts chapter 2.

00:09:26.880 --> 00:09:30.000
They were all of one sound and one accord.

00:09:30.000 --> 00:09:36.479
" And when they did this, there was, like they said, a sound like a mighty rushing wind of the Holy Ghost and fire.

00:09:36.479 --> 00:09:41.050
They all spoke in tongues, but they were all with one sound.

00:09:41.050 --> 00:09:44.434
It was with one sound, with one voice.

00:09:44.434 --> 00:09:48.880
And there's too much discord in the body of Christ right now.

00:09:48.880 --> 00:09:57.679
And the Lord said to me, "I'm taking down the walls of the barriers of religion for the day.

00:09:57.679 --> 00:09:58.640
There's a great shaking.

00:09:58.640 --> 00:10:14.079
" And I saw, just like in war times—I've warned you all—like in war times whenever in World War II how the women came and everybody came together and they worked together to create a community when the men were off to war.

00:10:14.079 --> 00:10:17.030
That's what I saw it be like in war times for the body of Christ.

00:10:17.410 --> 00:10:18.680
It's time for the body of Christ.

00:10:18.680 --> 00:10:25.920
It doesn't matter if you're Baptist, if you're Methodist, if you're Catholic, if you're charismatic or Episcopalian or whatever.

00:10:25.920 --> 00:10:27.280
It was the body.

00:10:27.280 --> 00:10:29.097
We all have different beliefs.

00:10:29.097 --> 00:10:31.839
We all think a lot different.

00:10:31.839 --> 00:10:35.480
But we all have the same common goal, which is that we love Jesus.

00:10:35.480 --> 00:10:44.540
We all love Jesus, and that's all that matters, and that we should be telling people about Jesus because the coming of the Son of Man is right at hand.

00:10:44.540 --> 00:10:47.966
He said, "I'm standing at the door, Brandon, and I'm waiting.

00:10:47.966 --> 00:10:49.988
What are you going to do to bring in the harvest?

00:10:49.988 --> 00:10:52.594
I'm leaving the ninety-nine and going after the one.

00:10:52.594 --> 00:10:56.480
For the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

00:10:56.480 --> 00:11:03.670
What will you do to help me bring in the harvest?

00:11:03.680 --> 00:11:06.177
" He cares and he loves every single one of you.

00:11:06.177 --> 00:11:11.257
He doesn't want any of us to perish, but all to come to repentance and have everlasting life.

00:11:11.257 --> 00:11:17.360
But the thing is right now, there's so many people that are riding the fence and that are lukewarm.

00:11:17.360 --> 00:11:18.320
They're lukewarm.

00:11:19.279 --> 00:11:20.980
And it's time to come.

00:11:20.980 --> 00:11:22.777
Either you're hot or you'll be cold.

00:11:22.777 --> 00:11:26.320
But if you're lukewarm, he said he'd spew you out of his mouth.

00:11:26.559 --> 00:11:33.298
Remember I told you in a couple of visions ago when I was praying, I saw the valley of dry bones and they were dead upon the land.

00:11:33.298 --> 00:11:36.480
And he spoke to me, and it was almost audible.

00:11:36.480 --> 00:11:41.040
And he said, "Brandon, can these bones live?

00:11:41.040 --> 00:11:42.639
Prophesy to the bones, Brandon.

00:11:42.639 --> 00:11:46.399
Tell them to get up.

00:11:46.399 --> 00:12:13.630
" And I saw as we prayed as a family—it wasn't about me, it's about us coming together as a family—and we interceded and I saw the bones coming together and I saw a Holy Ghost glow come upon the skin and it started sparkling, and I saw the head become the head and I saw the hands become hands and they all joined together and the valley of bones started to come back to life, and I believe a great, great harvest.

00:12:13.630 --> 00:12:38.720
I saw, and then I saw a dam that was full of water, which was the former rain and the latter rain all coming together, and there was a great mighty rushing wind of water, like water just flowing upon this valley of dry bones, and I'm telling you we will see the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen before.

00:12:38.720 --> 00:12:40.178
It's about to happen.

00:12:40.178 --> 00:12:48.359
I told you I saw the casinos and the people having meetings in the casinos in Las Vegas, and the glory of the Lord came in.

00:12:52.800 --> 00:12:57.280
It's time to get excited and have expectation about what God is going to do in this earth.

00:12:57.280 --> 00:13:01.920
Can't you see the signs of the times, ladies and gentlemen?

00:13:01.920 --> 00:13:04.240
It's all around you.

00:13:04.240 --> 00:13:15.110
But many people are like a frog in a pot and the water's heating up around them and you don't even know it's starting to boil.

00:13:15.120 --> 00:13:16.980
The end times is not convenient.

00:13:16.980 --> 00:13:20.982
I hear people say when I pray, I hear it: "It's not convenient.

00:13:20.982 --> 00:13:22.319
I don't want to live through this.

00:13:22.319 --> 00:13:23.519
" Well, we have a window.

00:13:23.519 --> 00:13:26.960
Donald Trump is here, but God said, "I've given you a window.

00:13:26.960 --> 00:13:30.880
I've given you a window of opportunity.

00:13:30.880 --> 00:13:32.910
What will you do with this window?

00:13:32.910 --> 00:13:34.310
Will you squander it?

00:13:34.310 --> 00:13:46.544
" As we see our brothers and sisters in South Korea have a president, a prime minister that is not good, from what they say, Canada, so many other places.

00:13:46.544 --> 00:13:48.800
It's serious times.

00:13:48.800 --> 00:13:49.867
It's a call to action.

00:13:49.867 --> 00:13:51.110
It's a call to prayer.

00:13:51.110 --> 00:13:53.059
It's just not of fear.

00:13:53.059 --> 00:13:55.617
I never come on here to tell you to fear.

00:13:55.617 --> 00:13:59.333
I never come on here to tell you to worry, "Oh no, the sky is falling.

00:13:59.333 --> 00:14:00.457
" I never say that.

00:14:00.457 --> 00:14:02.560
The sky is not falling, Chicken Little.

00:14:02.560 --> 00:14:03.840
It's not about that.

00:14:03.840 --> 00:14:06.720
It's about the body of Christ arising and shining.

00:14:06.720 --> 00:14:13.600
For the light has come and the glory of the Lord is risen on us.

00:14:13.600 --> 00:14:19.509
Being serious about our Father's business and preaching and telling people that Jesus is coming, that's what matters the most.

00:14:19.509 --> 00:14:22.939
All this other stuff, materialism and all this other stuff, it's crap.

00:14:22.939 --> 00:14:24.659
Who cares about it?

00:14:24.659 --> 00:14:27.097
God said he'd provide a window of opportunity.

00:14:27.097 --> 00:14:34.959
He told me, he said, "Brandon, I'll provide a window for the remnant that is listening to me, that is staying close to me.

00:14:34.959 --> 00:14:37.760
I'm not going to yell.

00:14:37.760 --> 00:14:40.249
" He told me, "I'm not going to yell.

00:14:40.249 --> 00:14:50.754
I'm going to speak in that still, small voice, Brandon, if you're listening to me, and I will tell you what to do, for the wealth of the sinner is laid up for the righteous.

00:14:50.754 --> 00:14:54.023
" And so many people are still not listening.

00:14:54.023 --> 00:14:58.160
He said, "So many people are asleep.

00:14:58.160 --> 00:15:01.004
" That's what I told you all a couple, like two or three videos ago.

00:15:01.004 --> 00:15:02.648
I saw the body.

00:15:02.648 --> 00:15:07.810
It was laying in a bed and there was an alarm clock that was ringing so loud.

00:15:07.810 --> 00:15:15.680
It was very loud and the bells were ringing, and the hands were at straight up twelve—straight twelve.

00:15:15.680 --> 00:15:27.920
And he said, "I've yelled and I've yelled and I've yelled for the people to wake up, and the alarm clock's going off, and this dispensation of time is coming to an end.

00:15:27.920 --> 00:15:30.222
But now I will shake to awaken.

00:15:30.222 --> 00:15:33.340
" And I saw the Lord Jesus go over and shake that body.

00:15:33.340 --> 00:15:37.440
And he said, "They'll wake up this time.

00:15:37.440 --> 00:15:41.1000
" Many people take a lot to get up out of bed sometimes.

00:15:43.040 --> 00:15:47.040
But this time the Lord said, "I'm going to get the attention of the world.

00:15:47.040 --> 00:15:48.959
I'm coming.

00:15:48.959 --> 00:15:56.870
I'm going to come and I'm standing at the door.

00:15:56.880 --> 00:16:15.759
" I just have an urgency in my heart to just keep being that voice crying in the wilderness, just like Paul Revere in the midnight hour, riding his horse telling you the British are coming, the British are coming, just like he did to the Minutemen to warn you that Jesus Christ is coming.

00:16:15.759 --> 00:16:25.179
I shout it on the wall warning you and telling you it's time to get your heart right before the Lord before it's too late.

00:16:25.179 --> 00:16:28.040
Many of you think you're promised tomorrow.

00:16:28.040 --> 00:16:32.846
Many of you think that you'll go to bed tonight and wake up tomorrow and everything's going to be status quo.

00:16:32.846 --> 00:16:38.230
But there's many of you that won't wake up tomorrow.

00:16:38.240 --> 00:16:53.350
Do you know, my friend?

00:17:04.160 --> 00:17:18.470
It's so awkward when it's live and I feel the anointing like that, and my son's usually able to help me.

00:17:18.480 --> 00:17:31.039
The cry for the man's soul comes through me to believe that every single one of you would know him, for you're running out of time.

00:17:31.039 --> 00:17:32.889
And many think we have so much time.

00:17:32.889 --> 00:17:37.029
I hear so many prophets say, "Oh, all this time America and all this stuff.

00:17:37.029 --> 00:17:41.760
" Folks, I'm telling you, shaking is coming.

00:17:41.760 --> 00:17:45.671
As I warn you about Israel, you see it today on the news.

00:17:45.671 --> 00:18:13.702
As I warn you about these things, and they're rioting in California, I warn you to pray—not a call to fear, a call to prayer—to get your house in order and get sin out of your life and stop walking that fence saying, "Well, you know, I want a little bit of the world and I want a little bit of Jesus, but you know, as long as I'm right there.

00:18:13.702 --> 00:18:17.520
" No, I'm telling you all, you're missing it.

00:18:17.520 --> 00:18:20.000
You better be all in.

00:18:20.000 --> 00:18:23.460
I'm sold out for Jesus today.

00:18:23.460 --> 00:18:28.960
It's time to get sold out for Jesus today.

00:18:28.960 --> 00:18:32.320
I told you to pray for Mel Gibson.

00:18:32.320 --> 00:18:36.023
I felt to pray for him, to keep interceding for this man.

00:18:36.023 --> 00:18:45.120
The Lord said, "I'm going to use him greatly in the days ahead, for he will help with this last push.

00:18:45.120 --> 00:18:46.537
Pray for his movies.

00:18:46.537 --> 00:18:48.093
There's a movie coming.

00:18:48.093 --> 00:18:50.559
" He said, "Pray for this.

00:18:50.559 --> 00:18:54.310
Intercede for him for fifty million dollars.

00:18:56.230 --> 00:18:57.389
" I don't know what that was all about for this movie thing.

00:18:57.389 --> 00:19:00.907
I see these numbers, I see these things to pray.

00:19:16.440 --> 00:19:16.720
He told me, he said, "Brandon, I'm cleaning up the church right now.

00:19:16.720 --> 00:19:21.280
" For judgment begins in the house of the Lord first.

